# 100 Days of Python 🚀

Welcome to my Python learning journey!  
I have recently started learning Python and committed myself to a 100 Days of Code challenge.  
My goal is to practice Python every day, build real-world projects, and grow into a confident developer.

## 📌 Objectives
- Learn Python fundamentals step by step  
- Stay consistent with daily coding practice  
- Work on mini-projects alongside learning  
- Complete at least one real-time project by the end of this journey  

## 📅 Progress
- Day 1: Introduction to Python – Variables, Data Types, Print Statements  
- Day 2: Conditional Statements & Loops  
- Day 3: Functions and Modules  
- Day 4: Data Structures – Lists, Tuples, Dictionaries, Sets  
- ...  
- Day 100: Final real-time project 🎉  

## 🛠️ Planned Projects
- Calculator  
- To-Do Application  
- Weather App using API  
- Blog Website with Flask/Django  
- Data Analysis Project  

---

⭐ Feel free to follow this repository to track my progress.  
Suggestions, ideas, or collaborations are always welcome!
